arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()
	
	local sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD_HEROIC
	end
	
	Events.SpawnRewardChest(CHEST_LOCATION, sChest)
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
-- if the mastery is failed close to the timer end, wait for the mastery failure to
-- finish before moving to cleanup phase
Hydra.Wait(0.5)
if (Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() == false and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idBoss))then
	Hydra.Wait(5)
end

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(flTimeElapsed)
	if not bStopSacrificeSpawning then
		for i, actorID in pairs(tActiveSacrificeSpawners) do
			Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(actorID)
			Hydra.Wait(Hydra.GetRandomFloat())
		end
	end
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
-- On mastery failure, spawn demons instead of the regular monster family
-- and make the succubus disappear

-- Delete all current spawners and kill remaining enemies
for i, actorID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS_ALL) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorID) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(actorID)	
	end
end

local idFXMarker = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_MARKERLOCATION, ID_THIS_QUEST, false, 0, 0)

Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idFXMarker, 32)
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFXMarker, FX_DEMONIC_BURST)

for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("LE_Sacrifice_All_Mobs")) do
	Hydra.ActorKill(actorID)
end

Hydra.Wait(2)
-- play fail conversation
Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_FAIL, idBoss)
Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idBoss, CONV_FAIL)
Hydra.QActorPower(idBoss, POWER_DEMONIC_DESPAWN)

Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idBoss)
Hydra.ActorDelete(ID_BARRIER)

local idRunes = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_MARKERLOCATION, ID_THIS_QUEST, false, 0, 0)
Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idRunes, 8)
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idRunes, FX_DEMONIC_RUNES, true)
-- spawn demon spawners
Hydra.Wait(1)
T_SPAWNERS_ALL[#T_SPAWNERS_ALL+1] = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_DEMON_SPAWNER_NO_MEGA, idSelf, false, 0, 0)
T_SPAWNERS_ALL[#T_SPAWNERS_ALL+1] = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_DEMON_SPAWNER_MEGA, idSelf, false, 0, 0)

arQuestPhases.szOnEnterScript:
for i, actorID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS_ALL) do
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorID)
end

for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, "spawnerCorpses")) do
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(actorID, 2)
end
arQuestPhases.szOnExitScript:
for i, actorID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS_ALL) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorID) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(actorID)	
	end
end

arQuestPhases.szOnEnterScript:
if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idBoss) then
	local idFXMarker = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ACTOR_MARKERLOCATION, ID_BARRIER, false, 0, 0)

	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idFXMarker, 20)
	
	Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(idBoss)
	Hydra.RemoveBuffs(idBoss, POWER_INVULNERABLE)
	Hydra.RemoveBuffs(idBoss, POWER_POSSESS)
	
	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup("LE_Sacrifice_Possessed_Mobs")) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(actorID, FX_DEMONIC_BURST)
		Hydra.ActorKill(actorID)
	end

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idBoss)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_SUCCESS, idBoss)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFXMarker, FX_DEMONIC_BURST)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(ID_BARRIER)
		Hydra.ActorAddToPrefabScopedGroup(idBoss, "LE_Sacrifice_All_Mobs")
	end
end

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idActorSpawned, POWER_INVULNERABLE)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(POWER_POSSESS, "CONTROLLER", idActorSpawned)
	idBoss = idActorSpawned
	
	--We know the boss is spawned so intro sacrifice monsters will be caught by the Spawn enemies possessed check, so spawn intro scacrifice
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "sacrificeMob1")
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idActorSpawned, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idActorSpawned, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetCollidable(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idActorSpawned)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idBoss) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(idBoss, 0.1)
		Hydra.QActorPower(idBoss, POWER_POSSESS, idActorSpawned)
	end
end

szUserFunctionsScript:
local function updateSacrificeSpawners(sGroup)
	if bStopSacrificeSpawning then
		return
	end
	local idSpawner = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(ID_THIS_QUEST, sGroup)[1]
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(idSpawner)
	table.insert(tActiveSacrificeSpawners, idSpawner)
end
szOnStartupScript:
ID_THIS_QUEST = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
idBoss = Hydra.ACDID_INVALID

tActiveSacrificeSpawners = {}
N_QUEST_DURATION = 90
bNoMoreSacrifices = false

Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_THIS_QUEST, "eliteMonster")
